docs.text: Changelog All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file. The format is based on Keep a Changelog and this project adheres to Semantic Versioning . 0.2.0-beta11 - 2022-01-31 Compare with 0.2.0-beta10 Changed Change methods path get_all_candles and cancel_all_orders ( a90698e by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta10 - 2022-01-31 Compare with 0.2.0-beta9 Added Add options and sandbox_token ( cfa20a3 by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta9 - 2022-01-31 Compare with 0.2.0-beta8 Added Add new field "message" to logging (#16) ( a47cb42 by TerekhinAO). Fixed Fix formatting ( dcc7bc0 by Danil Akhtarov). Fix: исправлена бага с преобразованием дат до 1970 года (#14) ( e750122 by Aleksandr). 0.2.0-beta8 - 2022-01-28 Compare with 0.2.0-beta7 Added Add getbrokerreport ( 7914d2d by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta7 - 2022-01-28 Compare with 0.2.0-beta6 Added Add use int as enum ( 52623e3 by Danil Akhtarov). Add generate docs ( a43f18a by Danil Akhtarov). Add changelog ( 2a1eb7a by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta6 - 2022-01-25 Compare with 0.2.0-beta5 Added Add init operationtype (#11) ( 4e79f69 by Dmitry Korzunin). Fixed Fix get_all_candles ( 46e2738 by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta5 - 2022-01-23 Compare with 0.2.0-beta4 Changed Change candle.value to candle.volume ( 1e2dc29 by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta4 - 2022-01-20 Compare with 0.2.0-beta3 Added Add ping message ( 672f1ce by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta3 - 2022-01-19 Compare with 0.2.0-beta1 Added Add script for download protos ( 51d179f by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta1 - 2022-01-18 Compare with 0.2.0-beta0 Fixed Fix requirements ( 54df63d by Danil Akhtarov). Fix sandbox env for tests ( 4187163 by Danil Akhtarov). 0.2.0-beta0 - 2022-01-18 Compare with first commit Added Add github actions (#3) ( 25fd10e by Maxim). Add logging (#7) ( 52bc22e by Danil Akhtarov). Add bidirectional stream examples ( 1f4ac09 by Danil Akhtarov). Add grpc wrapper (#4) ( 8e58eb1 by Danil Akhtarov). Add dev tools ( f1734f0 by Danil Akhtarov). Changed Change repo name ( ac874bf by Danil Akhtarov). Fixed Fix stream wrapper ( b5be10d by Danil Akhtarov).
